  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Grand Hotel Capo Testa is a luxurious hotel in a wonderful setting right beside the crystal-clear <a data-udi="umb://document/c7d9c305cd1e44568dec1178157bc9f9" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c7d9c305cd1e44568dec1178157bc9f9}" title="Sardinia">Sardinian</a> sea. There is lots to see in the area, from stunning white sandy beaches with turquoise waters to traditional Sardinian villages and up market towns. It’s just 4km from the typical Sardinian town of  <a data-udi="umb://document/7d2dc3f46ebb4517b6dbff2963ca3045" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7d2dc3f46ebb4517b6dbff2963ca3045}" title="Santa Teresa Gallura">Santa Teresa</a> from where you can catch ferries for day trips to Corsica. Set on beautiful sandy beach of Rena di Ponente, the hotel and its infinity pools have stunning views over the bay. A buffet breakfast is served each morning. In the evening romantic candlelit dinners can be enjoyed in the Colonna Restaurant, with magnificent panoramic backdrop of the entire gulf. There is also the Pagoda restaurant that serves buffet lunches and in the evening turns into a grill restaurant, serving meat and fresh fish. The comfortable rooms are the prefect retreat after a day spent in the Sardinian sunshine and exploring the area. They’re bright and breezy with light pastel tones and wooden furnishings. The have an authentic Sardinian feel with lovely views across the hotel’s gardens.</p>
<p>Car hire is recommended for this hotel.Grand Hotel Capo Testa is approx. 1 hour 15 mins from Olbia airport.</p>]]></description>
