  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong><u>Restaurants &amp; Bars </u></strong></p>
<p>The Colonna Grand Hotel Capo Testa has two restaurants that give guests the chance to try delicious traditional local dishes and as well as national and international specialties in front of spectacular views:</p>
<ul>
<li>Restaurant Colonna</li>
<li>Pagoda Restaurant</li>
</ul>
<p>The hotel also has two bars serving cool drinks and light refreshments, in the evenings there will often be a pianist paying at the bar:</p>
<ul>
<li>Bar Hall</li>
<li>Pool Bar</li>
</ul>
<p><strong><u>Pools &amp; Beaches </u></strong></p>
<p><strong>Pools </strong>The hotel as a series of swimming pools on different levels ad in different shapes and size. They seem to undulate and merge creating a series of small more private pools to cool off in a and larger ones for those who want to swim. There is a Large seawater infinity pool with a whirlpool.</p>
<p><strong>Beaches </strong>The hotel is located in front of the European Blue Flag beach of Rena di Ponente, one of the most beautiful white sandy beaches in northern Sardinia.</p>
<p>The hotel also offers an area for its guests, equipped with sun beds, umbrellas and beach towels and the possibility of practicing various water sports activities (payable locally).</p>
<p><strong><u>Wellness Centre</u></strong></p>
<p>The hotel has its own wellness centre offering treatments and massages (payable locally)</p>
<p><strong><u>Activities</u></strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Fitness Room</li>
</ul>
<p>Payable locally:</p>
<ul>
<li>Mountain bike hire</li>
<li>Sailing courses</li>
<li>Mini club for children aged 5 -12 years</li>
</ul>
<p><strong><u>Genreal Facilities</u></strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Free wifi</li>
<li>Shuttle service to the centre of Santa Teresa di Gallura (scheduled times and prior reservation required)</li>
</ul>]]></facilityDescription>
