  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Classic rooms</strong> are finely furnished in typical Sardinian style, using pastel colours and wooden furnishings. These rooms have a small balcony with table and chairs offering garden views. They can accommodate two to three people with an additional third bed or cot available on request. All rooms have balcony or terrace, private bath or shower, air conditioning, television, WiFi, minibar, safe and hairdryer. Third bed available on request. </p>
<p><strong>Superior rooms</strong> have a covered balcony and a partial sea view.</p>
<p><strong>Deluxe rooms</strong> have a lovely sea view.</p>
<p>Classic rooms for single use are available on request, please call to book.</p>
<p> </p>]]></roomsDescription>
